metadata.name: Urban Disconnect NFT Series | 02 London IllumiNation (/23)
metadata.description:
After the shock of New York a new great city rises up and exit the earth’s atmosphere. London.  
 
In this New Year’s drop titled ‘London IllumiNation’ the people of London await a new dawn as the city lights up in celebration.  
 
New cities and travel stages are minted weekly with varying release numbers so follow the Urban Disconnect journey to stay up to date on https://linktr.ee/urbandisconnect
